---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services — Plenum AI Systems"
  description="Five AI-powered growth systems for home service businesses: Database Reactivation, Auto Reviews & Referrals, Missed Call Text-Back, AI Sales Grader, Paid Ads Integration."
  canonical="https://plenumaisystems.com/services">

<Nav />

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Services</div>
    <h1>Five services. One growth system.</h1>
    <p>We don't sell a random tactic and call it a strategy. We connect the pieces that actually fill your calendar.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Service 01</div>
    <h2>Outreach Specialist — Dead Lead Reactivation</h2>
    <p>Your CRM database is full of leads you paid to acquire — and never contacted again. Up to <strong style="color:var(--text);">27% of businesses never follow up</strong> with their leads. That's money sitting in a spreadsheet doing nothing.</p>
    <p>We deploy AI-driven SMS campaigns that text your old leads with contextual offers. The AI handles objections in real time, qualifies interest, and routes hot prospects directly to your calendar. You already paid for these leads. This is how you collect.</p>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon orange" style="font-size:1.5rem;">⚡</div>
        <h3>$500 Market Test</h3>
        <p>Every engagement starts here. We reactivate a segment of your dead leads. If it doesn't produce ROI in week one, you walk away with zero risk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon blue" style="font-size:1.5rem;">↻</div>
        <h3>Automated & Persistent</h3>
        <p>AI follows up across multiple touchpoints. SMS, email, and voice — sequenced intelligently based on lead age, source, and previous interactions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Service 02</div>
    <h2>Reputation Manager — Auto Reviews & Referrals</h2>
    <p><strong style="color:var(--text);">98% of customers</strong> check reviews before buying. Only <strong style="color:var(--text);">11% of staff</strong> ever ask for one. That gap is costing you jobs — every single day.</p>
    <p>When a job is marked complete, a review request fires automatically. If the customer leaves a 5-star review, a referral prompt triggers immediately. The entire loop is zero-touch — your team doesn't have to remember.</p>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon green" style="font-size:1.5rem;">★</div>
        <h3>Reviews on Autopilot</h3>
        <p>Post-job trigger → personalized review request via SMS → direct link to Google/Yelp. You set the timing, the messaging, and the platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon silver" style="font-size:1.5rem;">R</div>
        <h3>Referral Engine</h3>
        <p>5-star review detected → instant referral SMS encouraging friends and family. Turn happy customers into your sales force.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Service 03</div>
    <h2>Website Manager — Lead Nurturing</h2>
    <p>A website lead is not a trophy. It is a timer. The moment someone fills out a form or asks about pricing, their interest peaks and the clock starts. Wait too long and they will not admire your website. They will open three more tabs and compare you to the competitor down the street.</p>
    <p>We follow up with new web leads instantly, answer common questions, and guide them to booking while interest is still hot.</p>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon blue">&lt;60s</div>
        <h3>Instant Response</h3>
        <p>Sub-60-second response time after every form submission. No delays. No "we'll call you back." Just instant, intelligent follow-up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon orange" style="font-size:1.5rem;">∞</div>
        <h3>Nurture Sequences</h3>
        <p>AI answers the questions people ask before they commit (cost, fit, how it works, what's next) and guides prospects toward booking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Service 04</div>
    <h2>AI Receptionist — Missed Call Text-Back</h2>
    <p><strong style="color:var(--text);">80% of missed calls</strong> go to voicemail. Most never get a callback. Every minute of delay costs 10% of your conversion rate. The phone rings, no one picks up, and that customer calls the next company on Google.</p>
    <p>When a call goes unanswered, our AI sends an instant text: <em>"Sorry we missed you! How can we help?"</em> The AI qualifies the lead in the same text thread, determines the urgency, and books an appointment — all in under 60 seconds.</p>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon blue">&lt;60s</div>
        <h3>Speed-to-Lead</h3>
        <p>Sub-60-second response time. Every time. No hold times. No voicemails. No "we'll call you back." Just instant, intelligent response.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon orange" style="font-size:1.5rem;">∞</div>
        <h3>24/7 Coverage</h3>
        <p>After hours, weekends, holidays — your AI doesn't sleep. Every lead gets answered, every time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Service 05</div>
    <h2>Marketing Director — Paid Ads & AI Nurturing</h2>
    <p>Paid ads should not just get clicks. They should fill your calendar. Most businesses waste ad budget by launching campaigns with no follow-up system behind them. A lead without follow-up isn't a lead. It's a donation to Meta.</p>
    <p>We connect your lead forms directly to our AI pipeline. The moment someone opts in — <strong style="color:var(--text);">within 60 seconds</strong> — they receive a text or call from your AI. The lead is qualified, objections are handled, and a meeting is booked.</p>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon orange">FB</div>
        <h3>Facebook / IG Lead Forms</h3>
        <p>Instant connection to Facebook lead ads. AI calls or texts the lead within 60 seconds of opt-in. No Zapier. No delays.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon blue">G</div>
        <h3>Google Ads Integration</h3>
        <p>Same pipeline, same speed for Google lead forms. AI qualifies before human handoff. You only talk to leads that are already warm.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="alt" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">Pricing</div>
    <h2>Infrastructure, not hours</h2>
    <p>You're buying a revenue engine, not consultancy. Flat setup. Monthly maintenance. No surprise invoices.</p>
    <table class="pricing-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th>What You Get</th>
          <th>Setup</th>
          <th>Monthly</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Silver</strong></td>
          <td>Database Reactivation + Reviews & Referrals</td>
          <td class="price">$499</td>
          <td class="price">$499</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Gold</strong></td>
          <td>Silver + Missed Call Text-Back + Lead Nurturing</td>
          <td class="price">$1,000</td>
          <td class="price">$1,500</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="highlight-row">
          <td><strong>Platinum</strong></td>
          <td>All Services + Paid Ads Integration + Custom Dashboard</td>
          <td class="price">$2,000</td>
          <td class="price">$3,000</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p style="margin-top:20px;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text3);">
      Every engagement starts with the <strong style="color:var(--text);">$500 Market Test</strong> — we reactivate your dead leads. If it doesn't produce ROI, you walk away with zero risk.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">What This Is NOT</div>
    <h2>No bait. No switch.</h2>
    <p>Before you invest, be sure we're a fit. This section saves everyone time.</p>
    <ul class="problem-list" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <li>
        <span class="num">✕</span>
        <div><strong>This is NOT a quick chatbot widget.</strong> Plenum AI is a full pipeline — phone, follow-up, reviews, and ads connected into one system that fills your calendar.</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="num">✕</span>
        <div><strong>This is NOT a lifetime SaaS subscription.</strong> Our month-to-month program means you're never locked in. When you're ready to move on, you leave — no penalties, no hostage situation.</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="num">✕</span>
        <div><strong>This is NOT for businesses that don't take calls.</strong> If you don't answer your phone, fix that first. We make sure every call leads to revenue — but you still need to close.</div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to stop leaking revenue?</h2>
    <p>Every approach starts with a free audit. We'll find the leaks. You decide whether we plug them.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">→ Book a Free Audit</a>
    <a href="/about" class="btn btn-blue">About the Team</a>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />

</BaseLayout>
